front.title: •Activate The Droids
front.gametext: Deploy on your Blockade Flagship (may not deploy on a site). Whenever you initiate a battle at a related planet site where youhave a battle droid, you may activate 2 Force or retrieve 1 Force.
front.lore: The activation of droids requires a transmission from a Droid Control Ship on a top-secret frequency. Only a Trade Federation captain has access to these frequencies.
